::'''Arma:''' Would you like to buy something, dear customer...? From the way you dress, you don't seem to be a prisoner or a guard... A rare sight, indeed!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} A customer? In this place...?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502020003-->
:::'''Arma:''' Haha, looks like you're not familiar with our group. In The Shackling Prison, everyone's my customer!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Someone opened a shop in The Shackling Prison?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502020005-->
:::'''Arma:''' Haha, looks like you're not familiar with our group. Prisoners are people too. Where there are people, there would be needs, and needs drive business. Our group's mission is to ensure you can do every sort of business in The Shackling Prison.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502020006-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502020006-->
::'''Arma:''' Apologies, I forgot to introduce myself. I'm Arma, chief executive of the Arma Correctional Group. You can also call me boss or shopkeep.
::'''Arma:''' Our group has been operating in The Shackling Prison for many years. We've produced many bestsellers that are popular throughout the prison, such as this Arma Correctional Body Wash. Not only does it remove grime and kill germs, but it also leaves the body feeling cool and refreshed...
::'''Arma:''' But, looking at how you're dressed, you must be a distinguished guest from another world sent here to inspect The Shackling Prison?
::'''Arma:''' A guest with your esteem probably won't like our group's shoddy products... But we do have products crafted with our prisoners' full ingenuity. You won't find these anywhere else!
::'''Arma:''' Why not buy something as a souvenir for yourself or a family member? I guarantee it'll be something that raises your prestige back home!
::'''Arma:''' By the way, we don't accept cash here. We can't spend them anyway. The common currency in The Shackling Prison is Trick Snacks, so you can use that to buy things from me.
::'''Arma:''' How is it? How can the Arma Correctional Group be of service?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502020002: Config/Level/Mission/5020200/Act/Act502020002.json-->
